metadata.name: Three From: Tokyo – Shibuya Crossing I
metadata.description:
I've had the good fortune to travel the world for many years thanks to my life in skateboarding and I'm excited to begin sharing some of the images I’ve captured along the way in my "Three From:" series.

Tokyo – Shibuya Crossing I is my genesis work of the collection and the first photo I’ve minted on my own contract. This is one of my favorite captures of all time because I’ve been able to return to it again and again and constantly find new details hidden amongst the layers of time and motion.

Please check this out on the biggest monitor you can find and enjoy the intoxicating energy that is Shibuya Crossing in Tokyo, Japan.
